      <title>图瓦卢选举结果推迟凸显气候影响</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/delayed-tuvalu-election-result-highlights-climate-impacts-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[图瓦卢的选举结果被推迟两周，因为危险的天气导致船只无法将新议员带到首都投票选举总理，这凸显了为什么气候变化是这个太平洋岛国的首要政治问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/delayed-tuvalu-election-result-highlights-climate-impacts-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 03:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被监禁的泰国前总理他信获假释——当地媒体</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jailed-former-thai-pm-thaksin-granted-parole-local-media-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体援引司法部长塔维·索松的话报道，泰国前总理他信·西那瓦已获得假释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jailed-former-thai-pm-thaksin-granted-parole-local-media-2024-02-13/</guid>
